---
title: Mushroom Ravioli with Kale & Walnuts in a Brown Butter Crème Fraîche Sauce
description: We love pasta in all its forms, but there’s something extra-special about ravioli—especially when it’s stuffed with earthy mushrooms. Here, we toss the tender pasta pillows with garlicky kale and toasted walnuts. It’s all served in a heavenly sauce of silky crème fraîche and rich brown butter, then sprinkled with Parmesan to bring home all those creamy, nutty notes. It’s pasta-tively delicious!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61e7026c0433292d6e4b275a-fb076db0.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/mushroom-ravioli-with-kale-walnuts-61e7026c0433292d6e4b275a-3606631b.pdf
